message.text:
𝐇𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐲 𝐁𝐢𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐝𝐚𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐚𝐮𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐁𝐫𝐚𝐢𝐧𝐬 𝐈𝐜𝐨𝐧, 𝐆𝐰𝐞𝐧! 🎙️✨

Known for her grace and energy, Gwen shines as both a voice of representation and a vibrant presence in every room she enters. 

Beyond her role as the Director for the Legislative Arm, her charisma and her warm personality reflect a beauty that radiates inside and out.

Her dedication to uplifting others, coupled with her strength in advocacy, makes her an important piece of the FEU College Y Club.

For that, we proudly greet our Director for the Legislative Arm, Jhazlyn Gwen R. Ite, a Happy Birthday and may this day echo our gratitude for her leadership, her voice, and her heart in Defying Limits.

#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27

Caption by Krista Belle Fernandez
Publication Material by Paula Ortiz, Janelle Tañedo

message.text:
𝐇𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐲 𝐁𝐢𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐝𝐚𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐚𝐮𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐁𝐫𝐚𝐢𝐧𝐬 𝐈𝐜𝐨𝐧, 𝐆𝐰𝐞𝐧! 🎙️✨

Known for her grace and energy, Gwen shines as both a voice of representation and a vibrant presence in every room she enters. 

Beyond her role as the Director for the Legislative Arm, her charisma and her warm personality reflect a beauty that radiates inside and out.

Her dedication to uplifting others, coupled with her strength in advocacy, makes her an important piece of the FEU College Y Club.

For that, we proudly greet our Director for the Legislative Arm, Jhazlyn Gwen R. Ite, a Happy Birthday and may this day echo our gratitude for her leadership, her voice, and her heart in Defying Limits.

#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27

Caption by Krista Belle Fernandez
Publication Material by Paula Ortiz, Janelle Tañedo

message.text:
𝐇𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐲 𝐁𝐢𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐝𝐚𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐚𝐮𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐁𝐫𝐚𝐢𝐧𝐬 𝐈𝐜𝐨𝐧, 𝐆𝐰𝐞𝐧! 🎙️✨

Known for her grace and energy, Gwen shines as both a voice of representation and a vibrant presence in every room she enters. 

Beyond her role as the Director for the Legislative Arm, her charisma and her warm personality reflect a beauty that radiates inside and out.

Her dedication to uplifting others, coupled with her strength in advocacy, makes her an important piece of the FEU College Y Club.

For that, we proudly greet our Director for the Legislative Arm, Jhazlyn Gwen R. Ite, a Happy Birthday and may this day echo our gratitude for her leadership, her voice, and her heart in Defying Limits.

#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27

Caption by Krista Belle Fernandez
Publication Material by Paula Ortiz, Janelle Tañedo

message.text:
𝑰𝑪𝒀𝑴𝑰: 𝑷𝒂𝒍𝒂𝒘𝒊𝒌𝒂 𝑬𝒙𝒑𝒓𝒆𝒔𝒔 𝒘𝒆𝒏𝒕 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒆𝒚 𝒄𝒂𝒎𝒆!

The 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐄𝐧𝐠𝐥𝐢𝐬𝐡 𝐋𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐮𝐚𝐠𝐞 𝐂𝐢𝐫𝐜𝐥𝐞 celebrated 𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐡𝐮𝐧𝐭 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 last 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟖-𝟏𝟎, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓, following the theme of 𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐰𝐚𝐧 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬.

The organization conducted different activities for its booth such as 𝑾𝒊𝒌𝒂 𝑷𝒂𝒅𝒂𝒍𝒂, 𝑾𝒊𝒌𝒂 𝑾𝒉𝒆𝒆𝒍, 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒑𝒍𝒖𝒔𝒉𝒊𝒆𝒔 𝒈𝒊𝒗𝒆𝒂𝒘𝒂𝒚!

Thank you for using 𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐤𝐚 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬, mga misis! Dahil sainyo aming sisiguraduhin na ang 𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐤𝐚 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬 ay mananatiling 𝑚𝑎𝑏𝑖𝑙𝑖𝑠, 𝑚𝑎𝑙𝑖𝑘ℎ𝑎𝑖𝑛, 𝑎𝑡 𝑚𝑎𝑎𝑎𝑠𝑎ℎ𝑎𝑛!

Caption by: Luis Miguel Rubinos
Photos by: John Matthew Pastores, Xienina Dizon, Iya Del Pilar

𝑰𝑪𝒀𝑴𝑰: 𝑷𝒂𝒍𝒂𝒘𝒊𝒌𝒂 𝑬𝒙𝒑𝒓𝒆𝒔𝒔 𝒘𝒆𝒏𝒕 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒆𝒚 𝒄𝒂𝒎𝒆!

The 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐄𝐧𝐠𝐥𝐢𝐬𝐡 𝐋𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐮𝐚𝐠𝐞 𝐂𝐢𝐫𝐜𝐥𝐞 celebrated 𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐡𝐮𝐧𝐭 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 last 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟖-𝟏𝟎, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓, following the theme of 𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐰𝐚𝐧 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬.

The organization conducted different activities for its booth such as 𝑾𝒊𝒌𝒂 𝑷𝒂𝒅𝒂𝒍𝒂, 𝑾𝒊𝒌𝒂 𝑾𝒉𝒆𝒆𝒍, 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒑𝒍𝒖𝒔𝒉𝒊𝒆𝒔 𝒈𝒊𝒗𝒆𝒂𝒘𝒂𝒚!

Thank you for using 𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐤𝐚 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬, mga misis! Dahil sainyo aming sisiguraduhin na ang 𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐤𝐚 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬 ay mananatiling 𝑚𝑎𝑏𝑖𝑙𝑖𝑠, 𝑚𝑎𝑙𝑖𝑘ℎ𝑎𝑖𝑛, 𝑎𝑡 𝑚𝑎𝑎𝑎𝑠𝑎ℎ𝑎𝑛!

Caption by: Luis Miguel Rubinos
Photos by: John Matthew Pastores, Xienina Dizon, Iya Del Pilar

The 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐄𝐧𝐠𝐥𝐢𝐬𝐡 𝐋𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐮𝐚𝐠𝐞 𝐂𝐢𝐫𝐜𝐥𝐞 celebrated 𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐡𝐮𝐧𝐭 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 last 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟖-𝟏𝟎, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓, following the theme of 𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐰𝐚𝐧 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬.

The organization conducted different activities for its booth such as 𝑾𝒊𝒌𝒂 𝑷𝒂𝒅𝒂𝒍𝒂, 𝑾𝒊𝒌𝒂 𝑾𝒉𝒆𝒆𝒍, 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒑𝒍𝒖𝒔𝒉𝒊𝒆𝒔 𝒈𝒊𝒗𝒆𝒂𝒘𝒂𝒚!

Thank you for using 𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐤𝐚 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬, mga misis! Dahil sainyo aming sisiguraduhin na ang 𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐤𝐚 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬 ay mananatiling 𝑚𝑎𝑏𝑖𝑙𝑖𝑠, 𝑚𝑎𝑙𝑖𝑘ℎ𝑎𝑖𝑛, 𝑎𝑡 𝑚𝑎𝑎𝑎𝑠𝑎ℎ𝑎𝑛!

Caption by: Luis Miguel Rubinos
Photos by: John Matthew Pastores, Xienina Dizon, Iya Del Pilar

The 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐄𝐧𝐠𝐥𝐢𝐬𝐡 𝐋𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐮𝐚𝐠𝐞 𝐂𝐢𝐫𝐜𝐥𝐞 celebrated 𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐡𝐮𝐧𝐭 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 last 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟖-𝟏𝟎, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓, following the theme of 𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐰𝐚𝐧 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐬.

The organization conducted different activities for its booth such as 𝑾𝒊𝒌𝒂 𝑷𝒂𝒅𝒂𝒍𝒂, 𝑾𝒊𝒌𝒂 𝑾𝒉𝒆𝒆𝒍, 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒑𝒍𝒖𝒔𝒉𝒊𝒆𝒔 𝒈𝒊𝒗𝒆𝒂𝒘𝒂𝒚!
